title: [Teorainn Valley, Brambles]
description: The brambles are so tall and wild they almost form a tunnel.  The narrow aperture between the brambles overhead permits just enough moonlight to illuminate the stony path.  A passing breeze fails to penetrate to the path but makes the long, sharp spikes of the brambles rustle slightly.
